Package net.proteusframework.core Description

Core API of the Proteus Framework.

This includes API for

  • automating tasks
  • managing data conversions
  • FreeMarker enhancements
  • GEO Naming
  • Hibernate Utilities and UserTypes
  • HTML models
  • HTML5 validator client
  • HTML entity escaping utility
  • java.io utilities
  • String manipulation API
  • Internationalization and Localization API
  • MIME Mail API
  • Metric API
  • Notification API
  • java.util.prefs.Preferences implementations
  • Progress API
  • javax.script helper API with some support for bytecode caching
  • XML parsing API and XML utilities
  • Reflection and miscellaneous utilities
